All words:
( ?[a-zA-Z]+ ?)

Email address:
[a-z0-9_]+@[a-z0-9]+\.[a-z]+

Ip address:
[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}
or
[[:digit:]]{1,3}\.[[:digit:]]{1,3}\.[[:digit:]]{1,3}\.[[:digit:]]{1,3}
#Code above only match ip addresses, but never check whether it is illegal.
##########################
Expression symbols
^
$
.
[]
[^]
[a-z][0-9]
?
+
*
()
{n} {n,} {n,m}
|
\
